Dependencies:
Assimp http://www.assimp.org/index.php/downloads installed to ASSIMP_HOME
DirectXTex https://github.com/Microsoft/DirectXTex/wiki/DirectXTex installed to DIRECTXTEX_HOME
zlib - can be installed via NuGet: Install-Package zlib-msvc14-x64
freetype https://github.com/ubawurinna/freetype-windows-binaries installed to FREETYPE_HOME